otautils

OTA Utility based on @iuss unpacker script [0].

Functions:

- Extract OTA Link from ADB
- Unpack OTA package into .img image partitions
- Flash images to device via fastboot
- Make TWRP flashable zip file

Run ./otautils.sh to get started.

[0] = https://gist.github.com/ius/42bd02a5df2226633a342ab7a9c60f15
